- New graphics;
- New controls;
- Synchronization for all devices;
- Sticker pack for iMessage;
- Apple TV App;
- Apple Watch App;
- GAMEPAD controllers support (MFi).

SUPAPLEX UNIVERSE:

For beginners:
- Supaplex (Classic) - Legendary classic Supaplex!
